{"tid":2509251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我喺呢度要同美國人作出呼籲","createTime":"2021-04-29T09:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T07:18:25.000Z","uid":251732,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"72965f2c7dcfac81ac1d14cfbb6d9e4ad9b98b41","tid":2509251,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"美國人，如果你唔想香港人當你哋係共匪敵人咁樣看待 ，請你哋立即作出一啲實質行動去反制中共在海內外的狂妄舉動， 尤其係支援海外港人建立武裝對抗共匪， 而家係時候要停止過去半個世紀， 為短期利益而所秉行嘅容忍政策。<br />\n<br />\n唔好對眼前嘅敵人有任何幻想， 我地在座所有人都睇實你哋！<br />\n<br />\nAmericans, if you don't want us all seeing you as enemy same as the commies, please take actual measures to counter CCP arrogant actions, ESPECIALLY PROVIDE ANY AVAILABLE ASSISTANCES TO HELP THE EXILED HONGKONGERS TO BUILD ARMED FORCES TO FIGHT THE COMMUNIST POWER.<br />\n<br />\nIt is time to stop this half-century long of appeasement policy for short-term profits. <br />\n<br />\nDo not have any fantasy to your enemy, WE ATE WATCHING YOU CLOSELY! <br />\n<br />\n- A DEMAND from Occupied HONG KONG <br />\n<br />\n#SENDTROOPSTOLIBERATEHK<br />\n#HKSOS<br />\n#LetMyPeopleGo<br />\n#HKEXITBAN<br />\n#GiveHKersArms<br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n#MilkTeaAlliance<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n#CCP_is_terrorist<br />\n<br />\n我們永不忘記 我們永不原諒<br />\n我們必定反抗 我們必定報仇<br />\n<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n剿滅匪類 刻不容緩<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n香港人 建國<br />\n天滅中共 全黨死清光<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfEgM9BVyyrUcLQBmZUE9ALXE3Zoh4dK7Gpuic7DkFREV?filename=wmuisoe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmuisoe.gif&h=6bce165d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfEgM9BVyyrUcLQBmZUE9ALXE3Zoh4dK7Gpuic7DkFREV?filename=wmuisoe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmuisoe.gif&h=6bce165d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfEgM9BVyyrUcLQBmZUE9ALXE3Zoh4dK7Gpuic7DkFREV?filename=wmuisoe.gif\" dat