IBERATEHK<br />\n#HKSOS<br />\n#LetMyPeopleGo<br />\n#HKEXITBAN<br />\n#GiveHKersArms<br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n#MilkTeaAlliance<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n#CCP_is_terrorist<br />\n<br />\n我們永不忘記 我們永不原諒<br />\n我們必定反抗 我們必定報仇<br />\n<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n剿滅匪類 刻不容緩<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n香港人 建國<br />\n天滅中共 全黨死清光<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmuisoe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmuisoe.gif&h=6bce165d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmuisoe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmuisoe.gif&h=6bce165d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmuisoe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmuisoe.gif&h=6bce165d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmuisoe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmuisoe.gif&h=6bce165d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmuisoe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwmuisoe.gif&h=6bce165d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"求人幫手用blackmail體裁?!"},{"pid":"d1e3e482587277a14b3c85ca0c1d279c61f8e002","tid":2509251,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"點解咁似之前一篇潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01155d79cce75cae111c95251376dde4bede0943","tid":2509251,"uid":313726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d93edc5eda8253d2631e1b8018f08c1326cb8f9","tid":2509251,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e88032da629143c1def2cc39b9cfce1739c06b1","tid":2509251,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d93